Johnny's Little Red Fire Engine
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

A man was walking on the sidewalk and noticed up ahead that little
Johnny was wearing a red fire man's hat and sitting in a red wagon. It
appeared that the wagon was being pulled slowly by a large Labrador
Retriever.

When he got closer to the lad, he noticed that Johnny had a rope
tied around the dog's testicles, which probably accounted for why the
dog was walking so gingerly.  

Smiling, he spoke to the little boy, "That's really a nice fire
engine you have there son, but I'll bet the dog would pull you faster
if you tied that rope around his neck." 

"Yeah," Johnny replied, "but then I wouldn't have a siren."

